title: Week Long Advanced Retreats
cleaned_text: Built upon the foundation of the Progressive Retreat, the Advanced Week Long Retreat is our most transformative experience. In the course of a week, Dr Joe demonstrates the limitless possibilities that exist when the mind, body, and spirit—of both an individual and a community—merge into one field of consciousness.
